skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill

des: Nasa News offers the latest flash updates delivered by Nasa. Nasa News is not affiliated with Nasa. add this as part of your daily flash briefing, then ask Alexa, "What's My Flash Briefing."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
